  "texts": [
    "Summarize the key findings from the literature review, emphasizing how IoT technologies are improving efficiency in agriculture, and discussing the potential benefits and challenges associated with their implementation.",
    "A bibliometric analysis of 78 articles on IoT in agriculture was conducted using data from Web of Science and Scopus.",
    "The VOSviewer was used to examine keyword co-occurrence and citation patterns.",
    "After preprocessing and standardizing terms, keywords with at least 5 occurrences and articles with a minimum of 5 citations were included.",
    "Out of 250 keywords, 246 met the threshold, forming 3 clusters with 16 co-occurrence items, 96 links, and a total Fig. 1 Review methodology link strength of 250."
  ]
}